episodes.title: RHOSLC Scandal: Is Mary Cosby Sill Running a Cult?
episodes.description:
Mary Cosby is facing explosive new claims as a forthcoming TLC documentary puts her church under intense scrutiny, alleging that the Real Housewives of Salt Lake City star and her husband, Robert Cosby Sr., preside over a religious organization that former members describe as a cult.

The church came under scrutiny when it was announced that Mary Cobsy married her step grandfather, Robert Cosby, Sr. and misconduct claims drug the Pentecostal church into the spotlight.
